profile:
My name is Derek Hurlburt. I proudly provide quality repair and remodeling services in Northumberland county. I am a reliable and insured professional that can handle whatever you need for your residential projects. I bring everything right to you so I can get to work quickly on any job, at any location.

Servicing all towns in Northumberland County including Port Hope, Cobourg, as well as Peterborough, Bowmanville, Newcastle, Oshawa, and Whitby. 

From small repairs to larger renovations work, your satisfaction is guaranteed. Call us today at 289-251-5709.
